function generateEZTemplateAuton(points){let codeLines=[];codeLines.push("// EZ-Template Auton Path");codeLines.push("chassis.pid_odom_behavior_set(ez::shortest);");points.forEach((point,i)=>{const x=point.x;const y=point.y;const heading=point.heading;const actions=point.actions;if(i===0)codeLines.push("chassis.odom_xyt_set(".concat(x," , ").concat(y,", ").concat(heading,");"));else if(point.direction==="fwd"){codeLines.push("  // Move to point ".concat(i+1));codeLines.push("chassis.pid_odom_set({{ ".concat(x," , ").concat(y," }, fwd, ").concat(heading,"});"));}else{codeLines.push("  // Move to point ".concat(i+1));codeLines.push("chassis.pid_odom_set({{ ".concat(x," , ").concat(y," }, rev, ").concat(heading,"});"));}if(actions.intakeTime!==undefined){codeLines.push("intakeMotor.moveFor( ".concat(actions.intakeTime," seconds, dir: 1)})"));}else if(actions.outtakeTime>0){codeLines.push("intakeMotor.moveFor( ".concat(actions.outtakeTime," seconds, dir: -1)})"));}//if (defaultActions().)
});codeLines.push("chassis.pid_wait(); }");return codeLines.join("\n");}export{generateEZTemplateAuton};
